videos.description: After defeating Ole Miss, Georgia head coach Tom Crean credits Anthony Edwards as an 'incredible teammate' despite struggling with six points on 15% shooting.
videos.headline: Crean defends decision of sticking with Edwards

videos.description: 13-seed Georgia takes down 12-seed Ole Miss 81-63 after Rayshaun Hammonds picks up his sixth double-double with 22 points and 11 boards.
videos.headline: Bulldogs get tremendous first round win over Rebels
